OL,3,CIn full: Every candidate declared to
OL,4,Cstand in Jersey's 2026 Election
OL,6,FThe full list of candidates standing
OL,7,Fin Jersey's 2026 election has been
OL,8,Fdeclared - with 92 candidates accepted
OL,9,Fby the island's Electoral Authority to
OL,10,Fstand in the general election.
OL,12,FIslanders will elect 49 candidates to
OL,13,Fserve as States Members in the States
OL,14,FAssembly.
OL,16,FThe election will take place on
OL,17,FSunday, 7 June, and will see the
OL,18,Freturn of Senators, who replace the
OL,19,Fseat of a single Deputy in each
OL,20,Fconstituency.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
