OL,3,CIn full: Every candidate declared to
OL,4,Cstand in Jersey's 2026 Election
OL,6,FVoters will elect a total of 9
OL,7,FSenators, who represent island-wide
OL,8,Fissues; 12 Constables (Connetables),
OL,9,Frepresenting each of the island's
OL,10,Fparishes; and 37 Deputies, who
OL,11,Frepresent one of nine electoral
OL,12,Fconstituencies.
OL,14,FHere is the full list of candidates
OL,15,Fstanding for each:
